author: Deccan
title: Vijay Babu reveals his Rambo look
text:
Deccan Chronicle | Priya Sreekumar | October 01, 2015, 00.35 am Vijay Babu Known for his astute business sense as a producer, Vijay Babu has proved that he can act too. He proved that he was good in serious, villainous and comic roles transforming into each role with ease.
His upcoming film Mudhugavu has him sporting a very different look. Vijay took to his social media page to share his look from the film in which he plays a don. He wrote, “Playing a character who is a fan of Rambo. The character is stuck in 80’s fashion.” And we must say that the Rambo look is indeed very intriguing.
